title: 108: The New Food Finds Haul Episode: July Edition!

description: In this week’s episode, Lisa and the gang are trying healthy new finds just for you! Finds like new dips, drink mixes, potato chips, chicken snacks, and SO MUCH MORE!!! Plus, a new peanut butter alternative that even Mikey liked! So what are you waiting for?? Jump in, and when you’re done, head on over to our Foodcast page for a list of the products!
